76561198015324296,Recommended,460960,35443294,Posted: 3 October,all,leuh gégé,"Very nice adventure game, wisely using the RPG Maker programming. I recommend it without any hesitation.The 3 different stories to achieve take place in well rendered historical English and American backgrounds (XIXth century and before).If you like detective games (although The Deed Dynasty is not one per say), if you enjoy paying attention to details on the scenes and in the dialogues, this game is for you, especially if you enjoyed the first act (The Deed). The Deed Dynasty is far more solid and a bit longer.All  your actions and answers may have unexpected consequences.There are many ways to end the game and this gives a lot of replay value to it untill you get the deed done and everyone convicted, but you ;)Even at full price it's a must have !"
